question.title: JPA - Can't insert into a table with a defined type (Oracle)

node.contents: I have the following problem: in my database there is a table that uses a defined type:

astNode.text: I have the following problem: in my database there is a table that uses a defined type:

elements.contents: CREATE OR REPLACE TYPE ARRAY_METHODS IS VARRAY (10) OF NUMBER (2);

node.contents: This column is mapped as List<BigDecimal> in its respective entity. The problem starts when I try to do an insert with JPA (I tried both persist() and merge()). Looking for a solution I found that I have to add the @Array and @Struct annotations:
